Description.Text: This is a quality hotel, for those who prefer a relaxing vacation. You'll also find tennis courts, watersports and a nearby 18-hole Golf course. (03/08 MQ)
The hotel is located on the beach, 16 Kilometres from the Airport, in the kukulcan Ave. with shopping malls and restaurants nearby at walking distance.
The Rooms are large in size with modern facilities and in very good conditions, all decorated in a contemporary Mexican style. All rooms have a large size bathroom in very good condition

There are five Restaurants and snak bars at the hotel serving a wide variety of cuisine from around the World. One of them is consider to be the best "Cajun cuisine" restaurant in Cancun with a live jazz band playing at dinner time.
The Lobby is large in size with plenty of seating areas and it is connected to the restaurant "Blue Bayoo"
